data.description: Welcome to this extraordinary 7-bedroom, 7-1/2-bathroom mansion that epitomizes luxury living at its finest. Nestled within the LeJardin community, this residence boasts an unparalleled blend of opulence, sophistication, and modern convenience.  The main level of the estate offers an array of spacious living and entertaining areas. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring state-of-the-art appliances, custom cabinetry, and a large center island, and a breakfast bar. The formal dining room is an inviting space for hosting lavish dinner parties or intimate family gatherings.  The living room is a showcase of luxury, with soaring ceilings, a magnificent fireplace, and floor-to-ceiling windows that frame panoramic views of the surrounding landscape.  The master suite is a sanctuary of comfort, with a spacious bedroom, a private sitting area, and a lavish ensuite bathroom complete with a spa-like soaking tub, a glass-enclosed shower, and dual vanities. Each of the remaining four bedrooms is generously sized, offering en-suite bathrooms and ample closet space.  Outside, the property is surrounded by lush landscaping, offering a serene escape with a private patio, perfect for al fresco dining or simply enjoying the tranquility of the estate. This mansion is not just a home; it's a statement of refinement, offering an unparalleled lifestyle for those who appreciate the finest things in life.  Venture down to the full basement, where entertainment knows no bounds. A fully equipped salon is perfect for indulgent spa days, while the gym provides a dedicated space for fitness enthusiasts. The bar area is a stylish venue for socializing, complemented by a playroom that guarantees endless hours of enjoyment for the younger members of the household.  Two bonus rooms on the basement level offer versatility, whether as additional guest quarters, a home theater, or a creative space. Two additional bathrooms ensure convenience and comfort for all.
